    "name": "Neoma",
    "profile": "Ecuadorian artist based in Denver, Colorado, with nuances of synth pop and indie pop.\r\nShe has captivated music lovers all over the world with her dreamy yet energetic “Lunar Pop” hits. \r\nIn 2017 [a8050451] hit the top of the Ecuadorian charts with her infectious single Real. Since then, she’s played concerts to thousands of fans throughout the Americas.\r\nIn 2018,[a8050451] relocated from Cuenca, Ecuador to Denver, Colorado, along with producer/bassist [a8050452] of Nockah and Vondye, to focus on her music career. \r\nIn June 2019, [a8050451] released, her first single as a resident of Denver.\r\nHer debut album, [r15703440] was released in November 2019.\r\n",
